A secret is not something no-one knows. A secret is something everyone knows is wrong. You can shout your secret from the rooftops but no-one will believe you. Until they do because you have built up in- evidence that your secret is how the world works. You will become a 5-year overnight success.

Knowledge is built social constructs.

A paradigm shift is a shift in social recognition of knowledge. The knowledge existed already but was not commonly understood across a social group. It was a secret.

People think that there are no secrets left in the world: the world has been discovered and each corner of it laid bare. In fact nothing is further from the truth. 